  <summary date="2023-06-08T17:06:55Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Future Logging Careers Act 

This bill allows individuals who are 16 or 17 years old to work at certain logging operations that are owned or operated by at least one parent or a person standing in place of a parent. Thus, the bill exempts such employees from child labor laws.</summary>
